data.description: 2 HOUSES FOR THE PRICE OF ONE! Private, secluded, heavily wooded, and super cozy!  This is a one of a kind property! 2 amazing houses for the price of one, 4 storage buildings, 4 acres, fenced yard, gorgeous scenery, and a huge pond to fish in! THIS. IS. IT!!!  First, the main house, 2,189 sq ft, has room for everyone! This is NOT your standard manufactured home at all! There’s almost no part of this house that looks, or feels like a manufactured home!  TONS of high-end upgrades! Two living rooms, an AMAZING Kitchen with true red oak cabinets, pull out drawers, an island, gas stove, refrigerator, and tons of storage, 4 amazing bathrooms with all new vanities, new plumbing fixtures, the master bathroom has a stunning new soaker tub, oversized master suite with attached office, workout area, or nursery room, 3 additional large bedrooms, 2021 HVAC, all new wall outlets, plugs, and covers, new lighting, a huge 2- car garage, new gutters, whole house water softener, whole house generator, large in ground storm cellar, an amazing back porch with wild life, peacefulness day and night, and so many more updates that I don't have room to list! You will fall in love! Next, the A-frame, which is PRACTICALLY BRAND NEW! This house is 762 sq ft, has 2 bedrooms both large enough to fit queen size beds, 1.5 bathrooms, its own backyard, utility room, amazing back porch, new flooring, new HVAC July 2023, all new light fixtures, new paint, new gutters, whole house generator, and electrical outlets and covers.  Seller willing to convey all furniture that is left in A-Frame as well, so if you need a house for a rental, your kids, your parents, or a separate office it’s all ready to go!! Don't wait!  This is a rare and amazing gem! Call today for your private showing! Seller willing to help buy points down as well!
